cs.NA, cs.DC, cs.SE, cs.AR, cs.PL 

This paper discusses resilience in numerical algorithms and fault models for handling silent data corruption. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NA (Numerical Analysis), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.SE (Software Engineering). The paper also discusses the need for abstract programming models, which falls under cs.AR (Architecture) and cs.PL (Programming Languages).
